{"type": "article", "id": 27928, "title": "没有灯泡的台灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-08T07:24:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702151803mUy5butl1zkiLKj0.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>没有灯泡也能叫灯？来自德国的设计团队巧妙地利用了手机的 LED 闪光灯，推出了一款名为 <a href=\"http://www.uplamp.com/\">UpLamp</a> 的台灯。放上手机，闪光灯发出的亮光就会均匀地散射在内部，涂上了荧光添加剂的内壁使得光线最终呈现出一种柔和的光亮。台灯还有一个内置的手势探测器，你可以通过拍手来控制台灯的开关，或是挥动双手调节灯光的明暗。目前 UpLamp 还在<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/uplamp/uplamp-the-first-lampless-lamp\">众筹</a>阶段，最低价为 49 欧元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151757k1WQAMoGtwj4csdm.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93235294\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151758ievSZP2xUXkauO1f.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021517590LplcknVfS3vuq1H.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 279px; width: 375px; left: 510px; top: 904px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151801DxVzgtLpORdnbfA1.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.742\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n\n\n"}